60|$|And {{while she}} broke the seal and perused the document, I went on taking my coffee (we were at breakfast): <b>it</b> <b>was</b> <b>hot,</b> <b>and</b> I {{attributed}} to that circumstance a fiery glow which suddenly rose to my face. Why my hand shook, and why I involuntarily spilt half {{the contents of}} my cup into my saucer, I did not choose to consider.|$|E
